satellite.heading: Satellite
satellite.specs:
Miyeso: 50x58x64 mm
1P PocketQube
Kulemera kwake: 245 g
Zida: aluminium, golide, fiberglass, ndi zida zamagetsi.
Orbit: Kutalika kwa 525 ± 25 km; kupendekera: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Woyambitsa: PSLV (Polar Satellite Launch Vehicle) yoyendetsedwa ndi ISRO

antenna.heading: Mlongoti/Sculpture
antenna.specs:
Makulidwe: 6 m (m'mimba mwake) ndi 1.2m (utali)
Kulemera kwake: 46kg
Zida: aluminiyumu, bolodi lowoneka bwino la epoxy, dome la golide la aluminiyamu yoyimitsidwa kudzera pamapangidwe opangira.
